race.comment: CANYA PONGA (7) was a convincing 25.59 winner at this track last start. In form and looks the one to beat again. WYONG DALLAS (1) scored by one length last time (25.73) in a Special conditions H over 460m at this track. Yet to taste defeat in eight runs from this draw. Can feature with the right run. MEPUNGA BROCKIE (6) has an excellent record over this course and distance having never missed the placings in five starts, including three wins and two placings. In the money last time at this track (25.83) in a Special conditions H, finishing a 4 length third. Looks one of the chances. WEBLEC JOEL (2) boasts a solid strike-rate over this trip.
